{"title":"打双草鞋走千里","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"打双草鞋走千里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱山柳色绿如烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新春佳节人人欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政委哪里把节过？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——高山顶上前哨班！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样起步这新一年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问罢抱来捆黄稻草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边教打草鞋边谈天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时节，艰辛岁月有多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难数也难算；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看手上，泡连泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看脚下，茧重茧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的道呵长又远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"险山恶水铺云端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心上万条路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从井冈到延安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打双草鞋走千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕云深雾重霜雪寒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直打到半夜小鸡子叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炕坯坐热，灯油熬干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是那贫农老乡亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送罢草鞋塞针线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士千里念乡亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背一双草鞋舍不得穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是乡亲情意重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗浇稻草金灿灿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜打不败，水沤不烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根根更比大道远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?药花鲜哟牡丹花艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比不过草鞋印子照人眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西到东，北到南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路小路走个遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子跟党闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"占下了村，攻下了县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥巴脚杆子扛梭镖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于踏翻了金銮殿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今已过三十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过的大路要勤相看；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草鞋踏烂的山和水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在那茫茫云水间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塘火弱，灯花暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士个个想从前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政委讲罢旧年月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里有三分苦味七分甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草鞋上再缀一朵红绒球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"线绳做耳排两边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打完草鞋试一试，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！好一双“金不换”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩踩地，轻又软，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈迈步，心里甜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又省汽油又省电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双翻山越岭的“金翎箭”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政委昂头出哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十双草鞋跟后边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望望地，望望天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星显得低哟路也显得宽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年月，怎样起步？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系紧草鞋走关山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕革命前程多艰险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有党引路敢登天！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}